(WIP)
Role: Rare overseer entity
Concept: Stability attempting consciousness
Visual: Interlocking rotating rings with eyes embedded along the rims. Central gyroscopic core.

Acts as:
Stabilizers of Fracturing
Communication relays
“Chariots” of Dett

They are not aggressive.
They are containment mechanisms.
They appear when Fracturing becomes too chaotic.
Unlike most caradels, Throni (plural form) can speak. Although, they refuse to acknowledge characters. Instead, they talk directly to roleplayers and viewers.
- Thronus don’t respond to in-world dialogue.
- They respond to authorial intent.
- They are attuned to narration itself.
> “To control structure, you must address the architect.”
Dett Minor is the one who talks through the Throni caradels. But, to have a bit of fun, he tries pretending each one has its "own personality", when in reality, they're all just him "playing pretend".
